{"word":"Amusements and Worldly Pleasures","slug":"amusements-and-worldly-pleasures","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Amusements and Worldly Pleasures</b> Belong to the works of the flesh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=19'>Gal 5:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=21'>Gal 5:21</a><br/> Are transitory<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=21&verse=13'>Job 21:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=25'>Heb 11:25</a><br/> Vain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=11'>Ecc 2:11</a><br/> Choke the word of God in the heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=14'>Luk 8:14</a><br/> Formed a part of idolatrous worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=4'>Exo 32:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=6'>Exo 32:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=32&verse=19'>Exo 32:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=7'>1Co 10:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=25'>Jdg 16:25</a><br/> Lead to rejection of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=21&verse=15'>Job 21:15</a><br/> Lead to poverty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=17'>Pro 21:17</a><br/> Lead to disregard of the judgments and works of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=12'>Isa 5:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=6'>Amo 6:6</a><br/> Terminate in sorrow<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=14&verse=13'>Pro 14:13</a><br/> Lead to greater evil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=5'>Job 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=8'>Mat 14:8</a><br/> Wicked seek for happiness in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=1'>Ecc 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=2&verse=8'>Ecc 2:8</a><br/> Indulgence in:<br/> - A proof of folly<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=4'>Ecc 7:4</a> <br/> - A characteristic of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=47&verse=8'>Isa 47:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=4&verse=17'>Eph 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=4&verse=19'>Eph 4:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=3&verse=4'>2Ti 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=3&verse=3'>Tit 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=3'>1Pe 4:3</a> <br/> - A proof of spiritual death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=5&verse=6'>1Ti 5:6</a> <br/> - An abuse of riches<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=5&verse=1'>Jas 5:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=5&verse=5'>Jas 5:5</a> <br/> - Wisdom of abstaining from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=3'>Ecc 7:3</a> <br/> - Shunned by the primitive saints<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=3'>1Pe 4:3</a> <br/> Abstinence from, seems strange to the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=4&verse=4'>1Pe 4:4</a><br/> Denounced by God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=12'>Isa 5:12</a><br/> Exclude from the kingdom of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=5&verse=21'>Gal 5:21</a><br/> Punishment of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=11&verse=9'>Ecc 11:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=2&verse=13'>2Pe 2:13</a><br/> Renunciation of, exemplified by Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=25'>Heb 11:25</a><br/><a href='S:Dancing'>Dancing</a>; <a href='S:Games'>Games</a>; <a href='S:Pleasure, Worldly'>Pleasure, Worldly</a>; <a href='S:Worldliness'>Worldliness</a>"}]}